{"tid":2019453,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"以後係咪冇得用阿拉伯數字?","createTime":"2020-05-16T09:40:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-16T09:53:42.000Z","uid":228820,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4a75fd60a802c2fa7829678c637a2f40ad7ed68d","tid":2019453,"uid":228820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T09:40:59.000Z","msg":"阿拉伯數字是西方或歐洲形式的印度-阿拉伯數字<br />\n阿拉伯數字始創於<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">印度</span></span><br />\n以後要用大寫漢字數字（零、壹、貳、叄、肆、伍、陸、柒、捌、玖、拾、佰、仟、萬、億）<br />\n一 二 三 四 五 六 七 八 九 十 廿<br />\n冇得用阿拉伯數字<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n廢是破壞十四億人既感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6b729e9dc646efe4e741a47c17bbc5892548330","tid":2019453,"uid":343361,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T09:44:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔係講笑<br />\n係有中文Programming 架<br />\n<a href=\"https://github.com/wenyan-lang/wenyan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fwenyan-lang%2Fwenyan&d=IqGrl%2FmL2I6%2Fp6gKwmVM%2BbZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=dbaaa5a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/wenyan-lang/wenyan</a></span>"},{"pid":"f0adbcaa2acc5c44f76d4a9affce86a1cbf9cb05","tid":2019453,"uid":228820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6b729e9dc646efe4e741a47c17bbc5892548330","tid":2019453,"uid":343361,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T09:44:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔係講笑<br />\n係有中文Programming 架<br />\n<a href=\"https://github.com/wenyan-lang/wenyan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fwenyan-lang%2Fwenyan&d=IqGrl%2FmL2I6%2Fp6gKwmVM%2BbZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=dbaaa5a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/wenyan-lang/wenyan</a></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T09:47:30.000Z","msg":"Ching 講多小小"},{"pid":"ffa07d780a523092929322474140028ef413c2ea","tid":2